---

<BaseLayout>
  <h2>Version History</h2>
  <Table data={versions} />

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <p>
    These are features I'd like to add in the future and if they are/aren't
    already planned in the version roadmap above.
  </p>
  <Table data={ideas} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    p {
        margin: 5px 0;
    }
</style>
